high_descs: Turn around and walk past the fridge to the corner of the cabinets.
Open the cabinet to the left of the corner and pick up the kettle.
Take a step left to the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink.
Turn left and walk along the counter to the stove.
Place the kettle on the front right burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed kettle on a stove.

high_descs: move to the counter to the right of the sink
pick up a kettle from the cabinet
move to the sink to the left of you
move to the stove to the left
put the kettle on the stove
anns.task_desc: Put a filled kettle on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk past the refrigerator, to the kitchen cabinets ahead of you.
Take out a tea kettle from the bottom, right cabinet under the counter.
Go to the sink to your right.
Place the tea kettle in the sink and fill it with water, then remove the tea kettle from the sink.
Turn to your left and go to the dishwasher, then turn left again and walk to the stove on your right.
Put the tea kettle on the front, right, burner, on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a water filled tea kettle on the stove.
